@NODE "Intro" "Introduction"
@{u}Introduction@{uu}

   KewlCDPro got a bit big on the configuration side, and people were starting
to have problems and get confused, so I thought I would write a Config Editor
GUI to solve these problems and more (especially updating from previous
versions). It has a simple GUI to edit the main config, and you can also select
Keyboard Editor from the menu which allows you to edit the new menu keys.

   This is only for registered users, so here's a good incentive if you haven't
registered yet!

@ENDNODE


