@NODE History "History"
@{u}History@{uu}

2.1 - Bumped version number to go with new KewlCDPro release.

2.0 - Initial release.

  * - Released a BETA version (#1).
  
      Re-wrote parts of the Keyboard Editor.
      
      Fixed problem with checking to see what keys have already been used
      <Marty>.
      
      Now selects the gadget that has a problem so you don't have to use the
      mouse so much :o).
      
  * - Released a BETA version (#2).
  
      The config pop-up button will now put the currently selected CD Config
      in the requester, also when you add a new item to the CD Config list it
      pops up the file requester automatically and uses the previous selected
      config in the file requestor.

      When quitting it now only asks to quit when the config has been altered.
      
      Default save files are now @{b}Doors:KewlCD/KewlCD.cfg@{ub} and
      @{b}Doors:KewlCD/Keyboard.cfg@{ub}.

      Activates the access string after selecting file requester.
      
      Changed FLE on/off to Archive enabled on/off.
      
@ENDNODE

